    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h3>Project Description</h3>
      <p>
        Sushi Master is a 2D match-three puzzle app for android. Players are presented with multiple ingredients which they must find matches for in order to complete the sushi recipe.
      </p>
      <p>
        The game is touch controlled and works on any mobile android device.
      </p>
      <h3>Project Team</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Becca Baird</strong>: Lead Programmer, 2D Artist and Sound Designer</li>
        <li><strong>Claudia Gunn-Harcus</strong>: Programmer and 2D Artist</li>
        <li><strong>Layal Saikali</strong>: 2D Artist</li>
        <li><strong>Shuyi Yang</strong>: 2D Artist</li>
        <li><strong>William Wu</strong>: Programmer</li>
      </ul>
      <h3>Software</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Adobe Illustrator</li>
        <li>Unity</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
